title: You want to hack Xbox controller ?  Postmortem on my attempts

In this video I do a postmortem of the 3 last weeks on my works to hack the X360 controller to be able to do QA testing on the Xbox. I have a small long term memory, I doing that for the community but also for me in aim to continue the project later when I have time and the good hardware that I am waiting.
